  ${
    $d x y z A $.  $d y z B $.
    iunon.1 $e |- A e. V $.
    iunon.2 $e |- B e. V $.
    $( The indexed union of a set of ordinal numbers is an ordinal number.
       ` B ` normally has free variable ` x ` as a parameter. $)
    iunon $p |- ( A. x e. A B e. On -> U. x e. A B e. On ) $=
      ( vy vz con0 wcel wral cv wceq wrex cab cuni ciun wss wi wal hbra1 ax-17
      ra4 eleq1a syl6 r19.23ad abid syl5ib 19.21aiv hbab1 dfssf sylibr abrexex
      onuni syl dfiun2 eleq1i ) CHIZABJZFKZCLZABMZFNZOZHIZABCPZHIURVBHQZVDURUSV
      BIZUSHIZRZFSVFURVIFURVAVHVGURUTVHABUQABTVHAUAURAKBIUQUTVHRUQABUBCHUSUCUDU
      EVAFUFUGUHFGVBHVAFGUIGKHIFUAUJUKVBAFBCDULUMUNVEVCHAFBCEUOUPUK $.
      $([14-Oct-03]$)
  $}

  ${
    $d x y z A $.  $d y z B $.
    iinon.1 $e |- B e. V $.
    $( The indexed intersection of a non-empty class of ordinal numbers is an
       ordinal number.  ` B ` normally has free variable ` x ` as a parameter.
       Note that ` A ` may be a proper class. $)
    iinon $p |- ( ( A. x e. A B e. On /\ -. A = (/) ) -> |^| x e. A B e. On ) $=
      ( vy vz con0 wcel wral c0 wceq wn wa cv wrex cab cint ciin wss oninton
      wex 19.42v isseti mpbiranr biex 19.11 bitr3 df-rex bitr4 nnull noel3
      3bitr4 sylan5b wi wal hbra1 ax-17 ra4 eleq1a syl6 r19.23ad abid syl5ib
      19.21aiv hbab1 dfssf sylibr sylan dfiin2 eleq1i ) CGHZABIZBJKLZMENZCKZABO
      ZEPZQZGHZABCRZGHVQGSZVMVSVLWAVQJKLZVSVMVQTANBHZAUAZVPEUAZVMWBWDWCVOMZAUAZ
      EUAZWEWDWFEUAZAUAWHWIWCAWIWCVOEUAWCVOEUBECDUCUDUEWFAEUFUGVPWGEVOABUHUEUIA
      BUJVPEUKULUMVLVNVQHZVNGHZUNZEUOWAVLWLEVLVPWKWJVLVOWKABVKABUPWKAUQVLWCVKVO
      WKUNVKABURCGVNUSUTVAVPEVBVCVDEFVQGVPEFVEFNGHEUQVFVGVHVTVRGAEBCDVIVJVG $.
